      "note": "名词到动词的转化，用作“穿衣裳”。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 2,
      "target_index": 3,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "穿上服装，引伸为承担职务或顺从规定。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 3,
      "target_index": 4,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "由“担任、顺从”进一步抽象为“顺服、信服”。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 3,
      "target_index": 5,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "从服从、适应到习惯环境。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 2,
      "target_index": 6,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "“服用”可指穿衣，进而指吃药。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 2,
      "target_index": 7,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_shift",
